com.mumfrey.liteloader

Annotation Type Priority


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Priority
    Priority declaration for LiteMods, used when sorting listener lists. Default value if no Priority annotation is specified is 1000.
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
